Live Football On TV Android App Privacy Policy
Introduction
Welcome to our Privacy Policy! We strive to collect as little data as possible when you use our service. We will only ask for personal information when we truly need it to provide a service to you and we will collect it in a fair and lawful manner. Fundamentally, your privacy is important to us.
This Privacy Policy gives you an overview of the data we collect and how it will be used.
